data.description: Stunning Windward Passage unit FULLY GUTTED & REMODELED from head to toe in the most desirable 01 stack with sweeping views of Kailua Bay and Lanikai mountains! The original 3 bedroom floor plan was converted to an elegant 2 bedroom showcasing an amazing designer and licensed contractor remodel with permits. Features all new electrical and plumbing, individual water shut-off valves for bathrooms & kitchen, drop ceilings with LED lighting and recessed fire sprinklers, sound proofing in primary bedroom ceiling, Hunter Douglas window shades, Bosch kitchen appliances, quartz counters with custom cabinets, custom built-in display in living room w/dimmable LED lighting, vinyl lanai door, luxury vinyl flooring with matching wood grain tile on lanai, and more! Two parking stalls, one covered & one uncovered, conveniently located on the ground level near the entrance.  The pet-friendly building offers numerous amenities such as a heated salt-water pool, jacuzzi, BBQ area, recreation room, tennis, pickleball & racquetball courts, fitness center with showers & sauna, pet park, surfboard/bike racks, resident manger and 24-hr. security. Close proximity to shopping, restaurants and Kailua Beach.
